description: Experience carefree living in this Tom French-built townhome in the heart of North Overland Park. It covers maintenance and more. Enjoy easy access to shopping, dining, and a neighborhood pool. This quiet location is near major highways and medical facilities. The home features a welcoming great room, a well-appointed kitchen, upper-level deck, and a main-level primary bedroom with ensuite. Refrigerator, washer, and dryer are negotiable.
